<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<!--@import "_head.kit"-->

<body>
    <!--@import "_header.kit"-->

    <main>
        <article class="project-detail">
            <header class="project-detail-hero section-fade">
                <div class="container narrow">
                    <a href="/portfolio.html" class="back-link">Back to portfolio</a>
                    <p class="eyebrow">Project Four</p>
                    <h1>Project Four title goes here.</h1>
                    <p class="lead">Use this page for a prototype, class exercise, or personal experiment that deserves its own context.</p>
                </div>
            </header>

            <section class="project-media-section">
                <div class="container">
                    <figure class="case-image case-image-hero">
                        <img src="/assets/images/projects/project-four-hero@1x.jpg" srcset="/assets/images/projects/project-four-hero@1x.jpg 1x, /assets/images/projects/project-four-hero@2x.jpg 2x" width="1600" height="900" alt="Placeholder hero image for the fourth project case study" loading="eager" decoding="async">
                        <figcaption>Hero image slot: replace with the strongest image for this project.</figcaption>
                    </figure>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="project-body-section">
                <div class="container detail-grid">
                    <div class="detail-content">
                        <h2>Overview</h2>
                        <p>Summarize the idea, what you built, and why it belongs in the portfolio.</p>
                        <figure class="case-image case-image-inline">
                            <img src="/assets/images/projects/project-four-process-01@1x.jpg" srcset="/assets/images/projects/project-four-process-01@1x.jpg 1x, /assets/images/projects/project-four-process-01@2x.jpg 2x" width="1200" height="750" alt="Placeholder for project four process image" loading="lazy" decoding="async">
                            <figcaption>Process image slot: research, sketches, planning, or concept exploration.</figcaption>
                        </figure>
                        <h2>Process</h2>
                        <p>Include what you learned, how you refined the interface, and what you would improve next.</p>
                        <figure class="case-image case-image-inline">
                            <img src="/assets/images/projects/project-four-wireframe-01@1x.jpg" srcset="/assets/images/projects/project-four-wireframe-01@1x.jpg 1x, /assets/images/projects/project-four-wireframe-01@2x.jpg 2x" width="1200" height="750" alt="Placeholder for project four wireframe or outcome image" loading="lazy" decoding="async">
                            <figcaption>Interface image slot: wireframe, prototype screen, or final outcome.</figcaption>
                        </figure>
                    </div>
                    <aside class="project-facts">
                        <h2>Details</h2>
                        <dl>
                            <dt>Date</dt>
                            <dd>2025</dd>
                            <dt>Technologies</dt>
                            <dd>HTML, CSS, Prototyping</dd>
                            <dt>Role</dt>
                            <dd>Concept and build</dd>
                        </dl>
                    </aside>
                </div>
            </section>
        </article>
    </main>

    <!--@import "_footer.kit"-->
</body>

</html>

